org.cast.cwm.glossary
Class BaseEntry

java.lang.Object
  org.cast.cwm.glossary.BaseEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, IGlossaryEntry, IWritableGlossaryEntry
public class BaseEntry
extends Object
implements IWritableGlossaryEntry

A simple, in-memory implementation of IWritableGlossaryEntry, based on the idea that a glossary entry is defined by an XmlSection. Applications wishing to store glossary words in a database (for purposes of referencing, etc) should create a different implementation of IGlossaryEntry and specify it when constructing the Glossary.
